# 核心 Unreal Engine 生成文件和目录
**/Binaries/
**/Build/
**/DerivedDataCache/
**/Intermediate/
**/Saved/
*.sln
*.suo
*.opensdf
*.sdf
*.VC.db
*.VC.opendb

# 项目特定生成文件
*.generated.h
*.generated.cpp

# 编译产物
*.obj
*.pch
*.ilk
*.meta
*.exp
*.lib
*.dll

# 日志和报告
**/Saved/Logs/
**/Saved/Crashes/
**/Saved/Profiling/
**/Saved/Autosaves/
**/Saved/ScreenShots/
**/Saved/Builds/

# VS Code 特定文件
.vscode/

# JetBrains Rider 特定文件
.idea/
*.idea
*.iws
*.iml
*.ipr

# Rider 缓存和用户特定设置
# 注意：.rider/ 包含用户个人工作区设置，通常应该忽略
.rider/
*.dotCover
*.shelf

# 可选：如果你不希望提交预编译的着色器或本地化数据
# **/Content/DerivedData/
# **/Localization/*/**.archive

# 平台特定文件 (示例)
# **/Plugins/**/Binaries/
# **/Plugins/**/Intermediate/

# 确保提交 .uproject 文件
!.gitignore
!*.uproject